  "description": "<p>An ergonomic road helmet that won't break the bank! 15 vents will keep you head cool when your legs start to burn. Outfitted with a MIPS liner you get adds an extra layer of protection. And for big-headed riders, the Idolo comes in X-large to fit head circumference 59-64cm.</p><ul><li>MIPS\u00ae technology (Multi-directional Impact Protection System) reduces rotational forces in an oblique impact. An inner shell sandwiched between the foam and the padding reduces the rotational torque on the skull</li><li>Inner is made of polystyrene, bonded to a polycarbonate shell</li><li>Dial offers horizontal and vertical adjustments to fit the helmet firmly to your head</li><li>Anti-slip cam dividers ensure the fit of your helmet remains perfect</li><li>Anti-allergenic interior padding is hand washable to ensure freshness</li></ul>",
